snippet.title: mediaXstanford
snippet.description:
mediaX is Stanford's catalyst for industry and academic research partnerships on the impact of information and technology on society.

Drawing on the world class capabilities of over 90 Stanford research leaders and their graduate students in departments, centers and labs across the campus, mediaX stimulates fundamental insights into innovation, helping accelerate successful outcomes.
